# ──────────────────────────────────────────────
# GainGang — environment variables
#
# Client-side public vars (EXPO_PUBLIC_ prefix)
# These are bundled into the app and safe to expose.
# ──────────────────────────────────────────────

# TODO: Decide on the GainGang backend/auth provider.
# The boilerplate ships with Supabase (auth + Postgres + realtime), which fits
# GainGang's needs (users, groups, daily goals, encouragement feed). If you keep
# Supabase, fill in the values below. If you switch providers, update lib/supabase.ts
# and context/auth-context.tsx accordingly.

# Supabase project URL (Settings → API → Project URL)
EXPO_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_URL=https://[project-ref].supabase.co

# Supabase anon/public key (Settings → API → anon public)
EXPO_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY=
